Resource Profile:

Official URL: http://koppeltaal.nl/fhir/StructureDefinition/KT2Patient Version: 0.8
Draft as of 2023-01-24 Responsible: VZVZ Computable Name: KT2_Patient

Copyright/Legal: VZVZ

The (FHIR) Patient (resource) is a representation of a person who is being treated by the Healthcare Provider to whom eHealth activities are assigned.

Usage:

  • Refer to this Resource Profile: KT2_CareTeam and KT2_Task
